      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question... im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i'm feeling super drained. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help with the energy and focus, since its just a natural herbal thing. is it okay to take them together or will that be a problem?",
